	<h3>RGB to hex conversion</h3>
	<ol>
		<li>Convert the red, green and blue color values from decimal to hex.</li=
>
		<li>Concatenate the 3 hex values of the red, green and blue togather: RRG=
GBB.</li>
	</ol>
	<h4>Example #1</h4>
	<p>Convert red color (255,0,0) to hex color code:</p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>R</i> =3D 255<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10=
</span></sub> =3D FF<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></=
p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>G</i> =3D 0<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10</=
span></sub> =3D 00<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>B</i> =3D 0<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10</=
span></sub> =3D 00<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></p>
	<p>So the hex color code is:</p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>Hex</i> =3D FF0000</p>		=09
	<h4>Example #2</h4>
	<p>Convert gold color (255,215,0) to hex color code:</p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>R</i> =3D 255<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10=
</span></sub> =3D FF<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></=
p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>G</i> =3D 215<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10=
</span></sub> =3D D7<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></=
p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>B</i> =3D 0<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">10</=
span></sub> =3D 00<sub><span style=3D"font-size: 0.8em">16</span></sub></p>
	<p>So the hex color code is:</p>
	<p class=3D"math"><i>Hex</i> =3D FFD700</p>
